Will I be able to create SEO-friendly and original content?

Absolutely. The prompts will help you to create even better original content.

And this is important because with Google's "Helpful Content" update, they're looking to penalize sites with canned, generic content generated exclusively for the purpose of driving traffic, not to be useful to humans.

Rest assured that The Blog Post Vault templates are not copy/paste content. Consider them a resource that will help you massively speed up your workflow and get better results with blogging.

You'll be prompted to share your own expertise and reminded to include important details so you can create business-boosting blog posts without ever having to start from scratch.

How does this compare with AI-generated content services?

In our experience, "artificial intelligence" (AI) content services work great for giving you a jumping off point - it's staring at a blank page trying to pull ideas out of thin air that slows people down. But that's really where the similarities end.

The Blog Post Vault doesn't have a "create content" button that generates copy you need to rework. Instead, it's a system of prompts organized by scope and complexity that are proven to drive traffic that leads to conversions.

And bonus! There are no monthly or recurring fees....you can use the templates as many times as you like, for as long as you're creating content for your blog.
